[normal]useful.
[normal]Q405 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mrs [bold]Glindon[bold]:[bold] Do you know how much the lack of skills is costing the taxpayer locally or nationally?
[normal]Mark [bold]Wardman[bold]: 
[normal]I do not think I would be willi
[normal]ng to put a figure on it.  Lack of skills means you are much more likely to encounter the risks that good procurement seeks to manage, essentially buying 
[normal]the wrong things
[normal],
[normal] or 
