[normal]quality, 
[normal]depending on your needs.  
[normal]All those so
[normal]rts of risks could be mitigated by having access to expertise.
[normal]Keith Davis[bold]: That is right.  It is 
[normal]very dif
[normal]ficult to get an overall sense of how much lack of skills might cost.  There are some case examples from things that have
[normal] gone wrong in contracts
[normal].  
[normal]I agree with Mark that the key area where there is a significant 
[normal]skill 
[normal]shortfall is 
