[normal]”  
[normal]We would look almost for third-party reviews of 
[normal]whistleblowing
[normal] policies to give public sector customers 
[normal]extra confide
[normal]nce in these contractors.  I agree with everything Alan said.  
[normal]W
[normal]histleblowing
[normal] is absolutely crucial
[normal] to combating fraud.
[normal]Q417 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]David [bold]Heyes[bold]:[bold] There is perhaps an irony in this.  If you depend so heavily on 
[normal]whistleblowing
[normal] to identify fraud, you almost depend on the fraud taking place for the 
[normal]whistleblowing
